/* eslint-env es6 */ /**
 * cache all active view models
 *
 * @module js/syncViewModelCacheService
 */import _ from'lodash';export let config={};/**
 * @param {Path} path - path
 * @param {Object} data - Value to set at the 'path' location.
 * @ignore
 */export let set=function(path,data){_.set(config,path,data);};/**
 * Get cached data.
 *
 * @param {String} path - path
 * @return {Object} get value if already cached
 */export let get=function(path){return _.get(config,path);};export default{set,get};
